2164.subject: MLML
2164.descrlong: MLML 251:Marine Geochem-  Geochemical processes in the oceans: thermodynamics of low temperature aqueous reactions, weathering, oxidation-reduction and biologically mediated reactions, and processes occurring at the sea floor and air-sea interface. Offered through Moss Landing Marine Laboratories (MLML); contact SEP program office for MLML registration procedures.
